&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain strong client relationships, acting as a trusted advisor on communications strategy and execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop creative ideas tied to product communications that generate high engagement and earned media and social coverage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing and mentor junior team members while contributing to team growth and capability building&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect and deliver integrated campaigns spanning product communications, brand storytelling, and cultural engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate product innovation and brand positioning into compelling narratives for media, consumers, and cultural audiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure alignment across earned, social, influencer, and owned channels to maximize impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
