&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Account Director&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Washington, D.C. team. This role will lead strategic public affairs initiatives that shape policy conversations, engage key stakeholders, and advance advocacy objectives while integrating earned media and communications strategies. The ideal candidate brings a strong background in agency public affairs or strategic communications, with experience working on Capitol Hill or within government highly preferred.&lt;/p&gt;
