&lt;li&gt;Be aware of industry organizations, advocacy groups, community partners, media, and other key external stakeholders to support strategic communications and public affairs initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive earned media strategies in support of public affairs objectives, including media outreach, messaging, thought leadership, and rapid response communications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee coalition-building efforts, community engagement initiatives, and public-facing events that advance client priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams across Burson to deliver integrated campaigns spanning public affairs, media relations, digital, and research.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities to expand client relationships and contribute to business development efforts.&lt;/li&gt;
