&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;More about the role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Burson India is seeking a motivated and enthusiastic &lt;strong&gt;Account Executive&lt;/strong&gt; to join our team in &lt;strong&gt;Gurgaon&lt;/strong&gt;. This role offers an excellent opportunity for someone passionate about &lt;strong&gt;automobile &lt;/strong&gt;communications, media relations, and brand storytelling. As an Account Executive, you will support the team in executing PR campaigns, media outreach, content creation, and day-to-day tasks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in drafting press releases, media pitches, and other PR content.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research media contacts and maintain media databases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor media coverage and create media reports.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support in planning and executing PR events or campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track industry trends and relevant news.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with daily administrative tasks and team coordination.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with internal teams to gather content or information.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in brainstorming sessions and contribute creative ideas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Embeds Burson proprietary AI tools as a core part of the marketing workflow — applying them to competitor research, content development, campaign performance analysis, and audience strategy to make marketing decisions faster and more informed.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay updated on social media trends and build relationships with key influencers and community contacts to optimize channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience that contributes to success:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ year of experience in the public relations or communications industry, preferably with automobile brands.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Public Relations, Communications, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You must possess a strong familiarity with how Generative AI tools are used across communications programmes, especially in planning, research, ideation, content creation, and daily operations to drive relevance and efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written and verbal communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
